Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's attachment at 1 is the vital point. It is at the \cf1\b center of the three stones\cf0\b0 .
\par This move is aiming at Black's shortage of liberties.
\par
\par After Black 2, White's wedge-in at 3 move works, so Black can't live.
\par
\par Black can't play dansu at 5, because of  the shortage of liberties.
\par
\par
\par }
