Dia. 02 Another Solution?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par There might be some people who think it is also possible to capture Black with White 1.
\par
\par If Black answers at 2, White's wedge-in at 3 works again and the result is same with \b Dia. 01\b0 . Again, Black can't play at A.
\par
\par
\par
\par
\par }
