Dia. 03 Black 1, Good
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Against White \'a1\'e2, Black 1 is a good move.
\par The useful proverb is here again: \cf1\b The opponent's vital point is my vital point!\cf0\b0
\par
\par After White 2, Black lives with 3.
\par White can capture the three \'a1\'e3 stones, but it is \cf2\b not enough\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par }
