Dia. 01 Black 1 is Greedy
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's connection at 1 is a greedy move. After White blocks at 2, Black doesn't have enough space to live.
\par After Black 3, White kills with 4.
\par
\par
\par }
